subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: A 3-pointer and free throw with 3.6 seconds left in regulation helped Stephen F. Austin overcome a late 10-point deficit and become the third No. 12 seed to win in this year’s Round of 64.
